# RAM Tuition Center - Direct APK Download

## 🎯 GET THE APP DIRECTLY

### **Method 1: Using GitHub Raw Content (WORKING)**

```
https://github.com/ramprasadray2026/ram-tuition-center/raw/main/app-release.apk
```

### **Method 2: Using Releases Page**

Go to: https://github.com/ramprasadray2026/ram-tuition-center/releases

### **Method 3: Clone & Extract**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/ramprasadray2026/ram-tuition-center.git
cd ram-tuition-center
ls -la app-release.apk
```

---

## 📲 INSTALLATION

1. Download `app-release.apk`
2. Enable Unknown Sources in Settings
3. Tap APK to install
4. Open app!

---

**Ready to use!** 🚀
